profile:
Welcome to WCH International Flooring Inc. We provide a wide variety of services and have over 20 years experience in the painting industry and 30 years experience with flooring. 

Tiling, flooring installation services, hardwood flooring, vinyl flooring, laminate flooring. 

Paint - Trim, Interior only, walls, windows, baseboards. We use quality paint products: Sherwin Williams, DULUX, and Benjamin Moore. 

Exterior Painting Services: Fences and Decks - staining and painting services  

Business Hours: Please contact us during our hours of 8:00 am to 5:00 pm Monday to Saturday 

Covid 19 - We are following the health and safety guidelines to ensure our customers and employees are safe.
